text: Calochone acuminata is a species of flowering plant in the family Rubiaceae. It is found in Cabinda Province, Cameroon, and Gabon. Its natural habitat is subtropical or tropical moist lowland forests. It is threatened by habitat loss. ==References== acuminata Category:Flora of Cabinda Province Category:Flora of Cameroon Category:Flora of Gabon Category:Vulnerable plants Category:Taxonomy articles created by Polbot Category:Taxa named by Ronald William John Keay
